<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">The History of... quests are exploration quests mostly but will require you to visit some dangerous areas for the later parts of the book.  The third part of the History of... books usually requires you to visit a Tier 3 or 4 zone to complete the sub-quest.  Example:  The Human book requires a visit to Deathfist Outpost in Zek.
<br />

<br />
More Heritage quests:
<br />

<br />
The Shiny Brass Halberd quest starts in Nektulos Forest in the Thexian Loyalists camp.  You need to learn Thexian to start this quest.
<br />

<br />
They alluded to a Manastone (!) Heritage quest in a recent patch message.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
